                "key": "Fangs Flying To and Fro",
                "string_values": [
                  "<p>Decreases Swimming Stamina consumption by 15%. In addition, for 10s after using an Elemental Skill, Max HP is increased by <span style=\"color: #37FFFF\">20%/25%/30%/35%/40%</span>. For every Hydro Elemental Type character in the party, Max HP is increased by another <span style=\"color: #37FFFF\">12%/15%/18%/21%/24%</span>, and the maximum increase that can be achieved in this way is <span style=\"color: #37FFFF\">24%/30%/36%/42%/48%</span>. Can be triggered once every 15s.</p>"
                ]
              },
